&lt;p&gt;This guide is aimed at local authority practitioners and is intended to be read alongside both local government finance reports and supporting documents which can be found on the &lt;a rel="external" href="http://www.local.communities.gov.uk/finance/1314/settle.htm" title="Local government finance settlement 2013 to 2014"&gt;local government finance settlement 2013 to 2014&lt;/a&gt; website. &lt;/p&gt;

