    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/simplifying-the-provisions-of-part-b2-of-the-building-regulations"/>
    <title>Simplifying the provisions of Part B2 of the building regulations</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This final impact assessment sets out the proposed changes to the provisions of requirement B2 of the building regulations relating to internal fire spread (linings).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;These changes are intended to reduce the burden of these provisions on thermoplastic lighting diffusers and decorative wallcoverings whilst maintaining adequate levels of safety.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This impact assessment updates the consultation impact assessment which was a supporting document for Section 1 of the 2012 &lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/building-regulations-access-statements-security-changing-places-toilets-and-regulation-7"&gt;Building Regulations consultation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
